nodes.bodyText:
@chtyim I don't think the codec-by-configuration approach will work for us because the default implementation of the LineRecordReader class always invokes this function:
https://github.com/apache/hadoop/blob/branch-2.9.2/hadoop-common-project/hadoop-common/src/main/java/org/apache/hadoop/io/compress/CompressionCodecFactory.java#L197-L213
This means that the codec is matched based on file extension, which is not a desirable behavior in my case.

